ActFederal-Provincial Fiscal Arrangements Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Agreement Concerning the Interpretation and Application of Section 25 of the Canada-Quebec Comprehensive Integrated Tax Coordination Agreement
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Finance to enter into an Agreement Concerning the Interpretation and Application of Section 25 of the Canada-Quebec COMPREHENSIVE INTEGRATED TAX COORDINATION AGREEMENT in order to to lower the provisional adjustment factor from 6.6% to 4.0%, for the interim years 2024, 2025, 2026, and 2027.
